    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "13-19. Abraham lifted up his eyes … and behold … a ram, &c.—No method was more admirably calculated to give the patriarch a distinct idea of the purpose of grace than this scenic representation: and hence our Lord's allusion to it (Joh 8:56).   ",
        "children": []
